# Docker build context excludes — keep it light + platform-clean (no host-native
# node_modules / venvs leaking into a Linux image; they get rebuilt in-container).
.git
**/node_modules
*-venv
**/dist
# …but keep the two @ka/core CLI bundles the ops distill tests (21/22/23) need.
# (re-include the dir so BuildKit walks it, drop its contents, then keep the 2.)
!kb/core/dist
kb/core/dist/*
!kb/core/dist/jsonl-reader-cli.js
!kb/core/dist/distill-result-parser-cli.js
**/build
kb/tools/mcp-opennutrition/data_local
runtime
raw
state
pending-topics
**/*.log
**/.daemon.lock
**/daemon.pid
ops/tests/results
.bundle-entry.tmp.ts
